    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;The presence of Constrained Application Protocol (CoAP) proxies may lead to infinite forwarding loops, which is undesirable.  To prevent and detect such loops, this document specifies the Hop-Limit CoAP option.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
